## Question

**How to create UDP socket connection in mesh network?**

========== Here is my SENDER(router) socket code ==========
```
ns_address_t address = {ADDRESS_IPV6, {0xfd, 0x00, 0xdb, 0x80, 0xff, 0x10, 0x00, 0x00,
						0xe8, 0x45, 0x5f, 0xff, 0xfe, 0x72, 0xc6, 0x24}, 8080};  
//this is my border router RF IP address
//(RF bootstrap ready, IPv6 = fd00:db8:ff1::ff:fe00:face)

void socket_callback(void *cb)
{
    socket_callback_t *sock_cb = (socket_callback_t *) cb;
	printf("event type : %d\n", sock_cb->event_type);
	printf("sockid : %d\n", sock_cb->socket_id);
	printf("interface id : %d\n", sock_cb->interface_id);	
	printf("len : %d\n", sock_cb->d_len);
	printf("LQI : %d\n", sock_cb->LINK_LQI);			
